NAME

    Monitis - Monitis (http://www.monitis.com) API Perl interface
    

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

EXAMPLES

    See 'eg' directory of this distribution for examples.

DEPENDENCIES

    LWP::UserAgent
    JSON
    Digest::SHA
    HTTP::Message
    Test::Simple


